  "detailed_description": "<strong>The Rangers in the South</strong> is a <i>PIXELART ACTION ROGUELIKE RPG</i> set in a beautiful 2.5D world inspired by the SNES classics. Fight and design a unique strategy with hundreds of alternatives to explore different biomes and challenges!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE</h2>Explore a hand-drawn world full of details, discover secrets and points of interest in a game that rewards exploration, with more than 5 biomes, procedurally generated environments, dungeons, and villages.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074110/extras/101f0b11c5cb4bd6438c29d3854d5d2e.poster.avif?t=1753283333\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074110/extras/101f0b11c5cb4bd6438c29d3854d5d2e.webm?t=1753283333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074110/extras/101f0b11c5cb4bd6438c29d3854d5d2e.mp4?t=1753283333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD YOUR CHARACTER</h2>No predefined classes, with hundreds of unique abilities, character traits, and procedurally generated equipment, you'll have to carve your path through hordes of enemies to make each character unique! Be careful, death is irreversible!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074110/extras/c82b2fc2d31daa4fbef1dc0f9d104218.poster.avif?t=1753283333\" width=608 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074110/extras/c82b2fc2d31daa4fbef1dc0f9d104218.webm?t=1753283333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074110/extras/c82b2fc2d31daa4fbef1dc0f9d104218.mp4?t=1753283333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REPLAYABILITY IS THE WAY</h2>Death will be your best teacher! Start new characters to discover new possibilities, items, and abilities. But not all is lost! Progress between each character is stored in the form of exploration, items, and gold!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074110/extras/745585e5a792b71c22e10f8cbac6227c.poster.avif?t=1753283333\" width=609 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074110/extras/745585e5a792b71c22e10f8cbac6227c.webm?t=1753283333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>The Rangers in the South</strong> is a <i>PIXELART ACTION ROGUELIKE RPG</i> set in a beautiful 2.5D world inspired by the SNES classics. Fight and design a unique strategy with hundreds of alternatives to explore different biomes and challenges!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE</h2>Explore a hand-drawn world full of details, discover secrets and points of interest in a game that rewards exploration, with more than 5 biomes, procedurally generated environments, dungeons, and villages.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074110/extras/101f0b11c5cb4bd6438c29d3854d5d2e.poster.avif?t=1753283333\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074110/extras/101f0b11c5cb4bd6438c29d3854d5d2e.webm?t=1753283333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074110/extras/101f0b11c5cb4bd6438c29d3854d5d2e.mp4?t=1753283333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD YOUR CHARACTER</h2>No predefined classes, with hundreds of unique abilities, character traits, and procedurally generated equipment, you'll have to carve your path through hordes of enemies to make each character unique! Be careful, death is irreversible!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074110/extras/c82b2fc2d31daa4fbef1dc0f9d104218.poster.avif?t=1753283333\" width=608 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074110/extras/c82b2fc2d31daa4fbef1dc0f9d104218.webm?t=1753283333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074110/extras/c82b2fc2d31daa4fbef1dc0f9d104218.mp4?t=1753283333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REPLAYABILITY IS THE WAY</h2>Death will be your best teacher! Start new characters to discover new possibilities, items, and abilities. But not all is lost! Progress between each character is stored in the form of exploration, items, and gold!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074110/extras/745585e5a792b71c22e10f8cbac6227c.poster.avif?t=1753283333\" width=609 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074110/extras/745585e5a792b71c22e10f8cbac6227c.webm?t=1753283333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>.",
